All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.CellEditor, javax.swing.table.TableCellEditor, javax.swing.tree.TreeCellEditor
public class GenericCellEditor<T>
extends javax.swing.DefaultCellEditor

CellEditor that uses a pair of functors to parse/format a value. Empty strings, or strings containing only whitespace will correspond to null values of type T.

Constructor Detail

GenericCellEditor

public GenericCellEditor(java.lang.Class<T> type)
Builds a GenericCellEdior using default format for the given class. The resulting editor can support any class that defines toString() and also has a one argument constructor that takes a String.
